<i>But it's hot as hell</i>
<i>in Philadelphia</i>

55
00:06:02,628 --> 00:06:06,689
- <i>Are you gonna open up a window</i>
- <i>Can't we compromise here</i>

56
00:06:06,766 --> 00:06:08,131
<i>Vote yes</i>

57
